      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "My apologies for the confusion earlier. The urgency at Apex Corp is dictated by the stock levels and our current inventory needs. I can provide a rough indication that our steel stocks are consistently high, and we tend not to hit stockouts with our strategic procurement plans. To ensure the best service for our stakeholders, precise and real-time stock information is critical. For accurate data, I can arrange for a systems notification or a secure connection to share sensitive stock status. Should you still feel this is important for negotiating a contract, I suggest contacting your manager directly for a more detailed status. Would you like assistance with this in any way?",
